data.description: Welcome home to a charming 2-Bed, 2-Bath bungalow! This home features gas cooking, sleek vinyl floors, and low-maintenance landscaping and the seller is offering the washer, dryer, and refrigerator as well. Commuting is a breeze, one mile from I-35N and it's 13 only minutes from Texas State University. Trace offers a beautiful amenity center that features resort style pool and a sand volleyball court. Don't miss the opportunity to call 137 Duck Creek Trail your new home!
